# `hhi` 1.2.0
## Calculate and Visualize the Herfindahl-Hirschman Index

### Changes

* Added the Journal of Open Source Software citation for the paper associated with this package.

* Streamlined a portion of the code for quicker and more efficient running.

* Cleaned up the description.

* Updated author affiliation.

## How do I get `hhi `?

The package is released on CRAN. If you have any questions or find any bugs requiring fixing, please feel free to contact me either directly (see the `DESCRIPTION` file for more) or by opening a ticket on GitHub. Thanks and enjoy!
